videos.description: LeBron James' sharpshooting is accurate early as he sinks the first points of the game for the Lakers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron sinks 3 from deep early) 2021/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron sinks 3 from deep early

videos.description: Montrezl Harrell puts Robin Lopez on a poster with this incredible two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harrell posterizes Lopez with electric two-handed slam) 2021/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harrell posterizes Lopez with electric two-handed slam

videos.description: LeBron James throws an impressive pass down the court to Kyle Kuzma, who passes to Kentavious Caldwell-Pope for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ridiculous pass from LeBron helps set up a KCP 3-pointer) 2021/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridiculous pass by LeBron helps set up a KCP 3-pointer

videos.description: Rui Hachimura throws down a breakaway jam as the Wizards have their first lead since the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hachimura throws down slam as Wizards take lead late) 2021/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hachimura throws down slam as Wizards take lead late

videos.description: After LeBron James appears to get away with an offensive foul, he passes to Alex Caruso, who drains a 3-pointer in the corner.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wizards in disbelief as LeBron isn't called for a foul) 2020/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wizards in disbelief as LeBron isn't called for a foul

videos.description: LeBron James hits a fadeaway bucket and draws a foul late in the fourth quarter, but he misses the free throw to leave the game tied.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron's clutch bucket ties game in final seconds) 2020/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron's clutch bucket ties game in final seconds

videos.description: Bradley Beal drains shots on consecutive possessions to put the Wizards up on the Lakers in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beal drains shots on consecutive possessions for OT lead) 2020/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal drains shots on consecutive possessions for OT lead

videos.description: Russell Westbrook is left unguarded as he gets the pass, drains the shot and is fouled with just seconds left.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Westbrook drains and-1 bucket to increase Wizards' OT lead) 2021/2/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Westbrook drains and-1 bucket to increase Wizards' OT lead

videos.description: LeBron James and Kyle Kuzma both miss shots in the final seconds as the Lakers fall to the Wizards.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron, Kuzma can't convert in final seconds as Lakers fall to Wizards in OT) 2020/2/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron, Kuzma can't convert in final seconds as Lakers fall to Wizards in OT

videos.description: Bradley Beal and Russell Westbrook combine to score 65 points as the Wizards win their fifth straight game by defeating the Lakers in overtime 127-124.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Wizards prevail in OT to hand Lakers third straight loss) 2021/2/22 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Wizards prevail in OT to hand Lakers third straight loss

videos.description: Despite playing more than 40 minutes Monday night, LeBron James explains why he doesn't think he needs to rest.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (LeBron doesn’t believe he needs more rest) 2021/02/23

videos.headline: LeBron doesn't believe he needs more rest
